<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī </hi>I<unclear>tuvu</unclear>moru pa<unclear>ṭi</unclear> <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> komā<unclear>ṟaṉ</unclear>caṭaiyaṟkku yāṇṭu 11 {built Over} 
<lb n="2"/>ṟṟūr nāṭṭut tirukkoṭikāvil<hi rend="grantha">śrīsarasvatigaṇapa</hi>tikaḷukku muṉṟu <unclear>n</unclear>ontāviḷakkerippa<unclear>taṟ</unclear>kku kuṭutta poṉ varakuṇa<hi rend="grantha">mahārāja</hi>r kuṭutta poṉ nūṟṟeṇpatiṉ kaḻa<unclear>ñcu</unclear> <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> Ippoṉṉi<unclear>ṉ pa</unclear>licaiyāl nicati nā {built Over} 
<lb n="3"/>yil Aḷantu kuṭuppomāṉom tirukkoṭikāvāṉa kaṇṇamaṅkala<unclear>ttu</unclear><hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> <unclear>i</unclear>tu paḻaṅkalpaṭi Inta <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vi<unclear>mā</unclear>nattile Eṟa veṭṭiṉamaiyil muṉṉi[[vā <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kam veṭṭikkiṭanta taṉik kallāl U<hi rend="grantha">bhai</hi>yokam Allāmaiyil {built Over}]]43 
